{comment: Verse 2}
Well, I [Am]want to make [Bm/A]love to you [Am7]tonight
[D/A]I can't [Am]wait 'til the [Bm/A]morning has [Am7]come[D/A]
And I [Am]know now the [Bm/A]time is [Am7]just right
[D/A]And straight [Am]into my [Bm/A]arms, you will [Am7]run[D/A]
And when you [Am]come my [Bm/A]heart will be [Am7]waiting
[D/A]To make [Am]sure that you're [Bm/A]never [Am7]alone[D/A]
There and [Am]then, all my [Bm/A]dreams will come [Am7]true, dear
[D/A]There and [Am]then, I will [Bm/A]make you my [Am7]own[D/A]

